Welcome to the TRI.0 Battle Tutorial for Velona!
Velona is a straight-forward combatant who can carry her own weight
With her high base stats, large MP pool, and well-rounded skill set,
Velona can dish out considerable damage while also keeping herself
healthy without the use of items.
Velona's default attack deals light magical damage.
Her real power comes out with the use of her Magic skills,
Velona has no gimmicks outside of being really strong!
She does have one weakness though!
If Velona's MP drops below 20%, her defense is cut in half!
